title: A Most Incomprehensible Thing: Notes Towards a Very Gentle Intro
description:
Title: A Most Incomprehensible Thing: Notes Towards a Very Gentle Introduction to the Mathematics of Relativity

Author: Peter Collier

ISBN-13:  978-0957389441

Included are epub mobi and pdf.

There are two epub versions included, one that was converted with default settings, and one that was converted with no margins.  The one with no margins was necessary for viewing on my phone, default looked better on a tablet sized reader.

Also in the mobi file, not sure the formatting of tables is done properly but I don't have a kindle, so if someone does please let me know.
